2DGame
======

2D Game using Microsoft XNA

This is a 2D work-in-progress Geometry Wars style of arcade shooter.

Implemented:

- Player WASD movement

- Player shooting

- Player rotating towards mouse

- Sound effects on fire

- All art assets incorporated but not all used yet

- Implement Horizon enemy (left<->right movement)

- Implement Vertician enemy (up<->down movement)

- Garbage Collection (anything offscreen)

- Barriers for player/enemies

- Collision detection

- Implement Chaser enemy (follows player)


TODO:

